            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h2>System Load 1.0.1</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>New in the details popup: <b>GPU</b> utilization + video memory, <b>Disk I/O</b> throughput, <b>Battery</b>, and <b>Thermal</b> state.</li>
