                <![CDATA[
                <h2>System Load 1.0.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>First public release.</li>
                    <li>Menu-bar CPU &amp; RAM with a CPU history sparkline, memory pressure, swap, network throughput, and top processes.</li>
